de.weltraumschaf.registermachine.bytecode
Enum OpCode

java.lang.Object
  java.lang.Enum<OpCode>
      de.weltraumschaf.registermachine.bytecode.OpCode
All Implemented Interfaces:
Serializable, Comparable<OpCode>
public enum OpCode
extends Enum<OpCode>

Opcodes of the byte code. General format: 

 [ opcode 1 byte ]
 [ opcode 1 byte ] [ arg1 4 byte ]
 [ opcode 1 byte ] [ arg1 4 byte ] [ arg2 4 byte ]
 [ opcode 1 byte ] [ arg1 4 byte ] [ arg2 4 byte ] [ arg3 4 byte ]
 

 TODO Make result register implicitly to 0.
